                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300708-109-off621 t18300708-109-cd622"></join>, 6 waistcoats, value 15s.; 3 brushes, value 3s., and 1 pair of shoes, value 2s., the goods of 
                     
